sal relations and\nbriefly explain their behaviour on a pair of typical examples from the\nKnowledge Representation literature. (Under consideration for publication in\nTheory and Practice of Logic Programming)\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Aug 2016 15:30:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-03"}
